Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: This Imperial corporal served aboard the bridge of the Super Star Destroyer Executor in 3 ABY. He had the nerve to interrupt a conference on the bridge between Darth Vader and three Imperial officers concerning the political situation in the Iskalon system to notify Vader that circumstances there required his immediate attention.
